  "video": {
    "name": "How to Make the Best Doner Kebabs",
    "description": "The Doner Kebab is a Turkish combination of meat (often lamb) that is seasoned, stacked in a cone shape, and cooked slowly on a vertical rotisserie. In this video, we teach you how to make the delicious dish, using garlic, spices, pita, vegetables, Tzatziki or Tahini sauce. Great for lunch or dinner, this is one unforgettable, savory dish.",
